sub_title: Postgraduate student MSc in Economics & Business with specialization in Financial Economics at the Erasmus School of Economics Rotterdam. Studied BSc in Economics at the University of Cyprus
summary:
Studied BSc in Economics at the University of Cyprus and graduated in June 2023. I am currently living in Rotterdam, as I am about to start my MSc in Economics and Business with specialization in Fianancial Economics at the Erasmus School of Economics in September 2023. 

Few things about me are that I love working with others and that I am a cooperative and social person.

So far, I have completed two internships, one as an Economics Development Intern at Blend App, and one as a Junior Tax Consultant at Taxand Cyprus.
